"+	Experience the bleak pollution<br />
")Poured over the summer glance<br />
"0Of the ghostly core, quick to disown<br />
"-Against those who I sink beneath.<br />
"<br />
"0The antagony shall gloss right above<br />
",And cast aside the degraded skin<br />
"0That atmospheres the desired eidolon<br />
"0Requested by many before this shift.<br />
"<br />
"5Ensure me, guarantee all that you commit;<br />
"7That the stars are green-eyed of our shine,<br />
"2That the heaven's dolphins begrudge us<br />
"6For sailing beyond their celestial sphere.<br />
"<br />
"-Plant your base neighboring mine,<br />
"5Hand-in-hand, hushed by the battle field.<br />
"3Transmit your aphrodisia into my veins,<br />
"2Make me suffocate without your poison.<br />
"<br />
"3Let you lead me to the frozen mountains<br />
".And shed the sky's charcoal layer,<br />
"1Where we can climb the annular stairs<br />
"-Of the star nirvana you promised.<br />
"<br />
"0Once used to be the lonely criminal,<br />
"4Having no one's hand to hold during your<br />
"0Sarcastic blasphemy, both you and I <br />
"3Held rusted blades to our own throats. <br />
"<br />
"1Unleash cupidity, interchange kisses,<br />
",Consume my closet diary-romance.<br />
"-Be the unwanted apostle beside me<br />
"/And equip yourself with admittance.<br />
"<br />
"/Quench my hunger for savaged amour,<br />
"3Send me blind with your mist of desire.<br />
".Find me within your enigmatic maze<br />
"3Emphasized of dried leaves to symbolize<br />
"4Your fading love for her vanished ghost.<br />
"<br />
"1Down on my bended knees in surrender,<br />
"3You gave me the mercy that pitied these<br />
"2Raging lamentations for random notice.<br />
"5Stated that there were moons in my tears.<br />
"<br />
"7Continue nourishing me with your adoration.<br />
":Don't stop giving me the lusting toxic I need.<br />
"6Hold me close beneath your defensive arms,<br />
"8As to encourage me in your void of security.<br />
"<br />
".You and I can chase the weak away.<br />
"7Scar each other to immortalize the avidity.<br />
"+Embrace the sympathetic memoirs<br />
"/Before we end our demolished skies.<br />
"<br />
"3So devour this emptiness behind my ribs<br />
"7And shed the days of recollected heartache.<br />
"9Shape me vulnerable enough that when we kiss,<br />
"8Parts of my phantom shall die a minor death.<br />
