"0Title: Billy by Day Old Hate at All poetry
"
"…	Billy went to a party, and got totally loaded. He was so loaded, that he could barley walk, or even speak. His words were slurred, and he stumbled. His friend came. His friends name was Frank. Frank offered Billy some acid. Billy said, “eih, Iss druk so I do.” Billy did the acid. Billy felt no different. 5 minutes went by, and Billy started feeling strange. The walls began to bleed around him, and he felt as if he was in a tornado that was not moving. He looked up to the ceiling, and it wasn’t there. All he saw was clouds and thunder. Fish began to swim around the room. The clouds started forming into a big wind demon, and started trying to get him. So Billy stood up, and tried to run, but there was a current. He couldn’t run. He got scared. He ran to the corner of the room, and leaned against the wall. Blood started drip down off of him. He got so scared that he ran into the bathroom, it taking about 1 hour to go the next room. Then he sat in the corner and shook back and forth. Demons started coming out of the walls. Billy got so scared that he grabbed the pair of scissors from the counter, and stabbed himself in the chest. Billy died.
"End of Poem
