"
"	<br />
"USometimes I feel life requires me to write a selection of wants and needs<br />
"FTo be posted like an ad engraved in the pages of the wind.<br />
"5I often wonder how my piece would read...<br />
"<br />
"<br />
"<Elly is an open book, perhaps yes and maybe no. <br />
"KReading the preface is not knowing, for I am more than I admit.<br />
"QI want a reader who knows the best lines are those that can't be seen<br />
"MThe truth of who I am is meaningless if you get lost in the pain <br />
"MWithin the novel my words run deeper, bleeding between the script<br />
"]A writer is suggested to fill in the blanks of what will be the greatest chapter.<br />
"[Don't try to discover my world if you're not willing this world to discover you<br />
"OJourney with me and realize many things are guarded in the darkness<br />
"8My talents and wounds will only expose yours<br />
">Approach me only if risks are part of your taking.<br />
"MMy memories are better suited in pictures running through my mind<br />
"EHanging on pondering walls framed in delicate sensitivity<br />
"RLet photography be the tool in which you capture moments spent with me<br />
"FPaint my suffering in colors only known to brushes of love<br />
"IHues that replace the hurt with soothing emotions of new care<br />
"PArtistic hands will cure ailments, forever becoming my only medicine<br />
"TThe stem of desire is only appealing if it runs far beneath the surface.<br />
"FKnowledge is wanted, I must know the root of your passion.<br />
"HMy soul is but a flame sparking erotica with steaming dances<br />
"6Beauty is only admired here but never felt<br />
