"<br />
"HI race toward the bridge of christianity and brake suddenly <br />
"HMy heart had an earthquake and the walls came tumbling down <br />
"CThe debree of such a mess tore the passage to my safety<br />
"ADesperation sores my thoughts and smudges my clarity <br />
"<br />
"HCircling around trying to decide which way to move from harm<br />
"LI look back only to see the devastation and erosion of the trail<br />
