"$do it now pay your due".<br />
"lThis feeling is so wretched so demanding at times it gets me to do horrible things to myself... <br />
"RI try and fight against it I try to push it back and push it under....<br />
"XYet at the sunrise of each new day this feeling awakes me with it's thunder.<br />
"ˆThis feeling never goes away it's constantly looking to feed upon my joy and my happiness making me feel as if I deserve none....<br />
"zThat the pain in my heart is there for a reason that it is there because I deserve to suffer until I am done. <br />
"‡In the midst of all this there is another feeling very shyly it speaks up it says good things to me it tells me I should live...<br />
"OBut I am constanly confused between the negative and the positive. <br />
"wI am more apt to follow the negative feeling for it speaks so loudly, it sounds and feels as if its right, <br />
"oYet when I have done what it asks of me it stays silent so silent and so begins the inner fight....<br />
"„I finally hear the other telling me I did wrong I shouldn't have bled to find relief and when this happens so does my grief. <br />
"<What is this weakness that lets me be deceived? <br />
"HWhy is it that I can't tell the difference between the two? <br />
"ILove I turn to you help me and with your support let my soul renew.
