"	Lady Sunset<br />
"<br />
" &nbsp;<br />
"#A Rainbow without laws.<br />
"/Teasing and playing as she pleases.<br />
"8Flaunting her many shades this way and that.<br />
"+Notorious where ever she steps,<br />
"%For her beauty and grace.<br />
"8Though she is different in every man’s eyes.<br />
