".Of the wonder that is Lady Sunset.<br />
"<br />
"J~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />
"<br />
"<She will brighten your day in its darkest hours.<br />
"6Filling every last bit with radiant color.<br />
"AShe brings you your last smile before darkness falls.<br />
"/A smile that will not fade quickly.<br />
"NHer very breath, like a California breeze, oh so sweet on my skin.<br />
"AIt's a feeling that only true Lady Sunsets can bring.<br />
"=A feeling of returning to a place long forgotten,<br />
"%A place of your very own.<br />
"@A feeling of home inside, no matter where you stand.<br />
"<br />
":~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />
"<br />
"lHer shape, perfect as it is, catches the eye, turning it from the sun in its final golden stage.<br />
"IShe challenges its beauty with her own and gets it to submit.<br />
"[The perfect shape, now outlined, silhouetted yet glistening, by a golden shine.<br />
"-Forming to her curvaceous design.<br />
"0An awe, a hush, as the figure fades.<br />
":Fades out of your life as quickly as she came.<br />
"*Swimming now, in the cool sea.<br />
"4Body glistening by the accompanying sun.<br />
"6Out of our lives the Golden Goddess swims.<br />
":Only to take shape as another beauty the next night.
