"3	As I walk in the valley of my thoughts<br />
"8I wonder why these surroundings seem strange<br />
"7I look up to the sky and see swirls of pain<br />
")I wonder if it will ever end.<br />
"<br />
"9The trees sway as I breathe out my deep sighs<br />
