"1Title: Rachel by Lil Punkette at All poetry
"
"		Rachel why the hell did you do this to me? I was 9 and you were 15. You told me to go to your room and pick out whatever i want'd clothes shoes,cd's. I choose some of clothes, and your monkey,Bob. I still have that monkey. You told me you were taking a shower. 45 mintues later i realized that there had never been any water running. The bathroom door was locked, you never did that, you always left it unlocked so that i could always go in and talk to you if i needed to. That was the second thing that i realized was wrong. I ran back into your room, to your make-up case where you kept your blades when you cut. The way i deal with things now, for the past two years, and i learned it all from you. You used to sew with needle and thread thru your palms. You'd freak out and i would have to get it out for you. Your blades weren't there. i freaked out, i ran to the bathroom and it was still locked. there was no noise when i screamed out your name. It came out whiny and scared, which i hated but i was scared. At your house the linen closet was conntected to the bathroom and you could get into the bathroom thru the linen closet. i got it cabnit openedand crawled thru to the bathroom. You were sprawled out your wrists were slit blood all over the bathtub. Your white cami and white boxer soaked with blood. All i could do was cry and curse myself for beign so stupid and not realizing what you were doing. I started cutting after that. your best friend came by to pick us up to go to the mall, she saw me cradeling your head crying. she called 911. she saved you. I keep my hands on your wrists to try and stop the blood it eventually stopped. You left a two years later. A few months after that you killed yourself. You huant my dreams i always see you covered in blood. tehn i see myself in a mirror. Wearing the outfit you picked out for me with my hair in braids down my back you loved my long hair. After you died i cut it all off. I went numb. then my other best friend deid in a bus wreck i went even number after you died. Then my friend called me and told me that she was going to kill herself. &nbsp;talked her out of it and now im writing this because i cut afterwards and now alot of people are mad at me. But rachel i was mad at you for dying. For teaching me how to cut and how to hide it. how to make the scars not noticable. but i've finally forgiven you after all that you've done...i still love you sis.
"End of Poem
"NTitle: The Dramatic  Bitch, my best friend by Lil Punkette at All poetry
"
"Y	Your the supposed "perfect" one, i hate you. you dont go thru anyhting that i go thru. you have it so fucking easy. Your lifes just so damn hard,But you don't have it as bad as i do. you dont have to deal with getting hit for rolling your eyes, thrown out of your room because you asked why all of your uncles girlfriends kids were in you room. getting choked for not eating, being accused of having an eating disorder 24/7, i cut to deal with pain, you cut for drama. you make everything so god damn dramatic.I try so hard to make you happy, but i'm never good enough for you, i'm just a little rag doll you pick and drop again because it's fun and your bored. You always call me not caring about how many cell minutes im using, and when i call you asking for some quick advice you cant talk. You stole my guy, my best friend i was finally getting the nerve to tell him how i feel and then *boom* you found out and then you had intrest in him. Everything that went wrong with you two was my fault i was flirting to much with him, then one day i got pissed and told you the truth...I was never just his friend but i was never really his girlfriend...with things like that they have to end good or bad, we never ended and you knew that so it's your own fault for getting in the way...i hate you...everything's always about you, your selfish, over-dramatic,rude. <br />
"<br />
"7You Are A Bitch And I Deserve Better Than You....
"End of Poem
