"Á	I take the blade to my wrist...the hurts become to much for me. I don't understand these things, I don't get my feelings, I don't get why you mean so much to me, You don't get why i do this, your always there for me, yet your not. You said that I could tell you everything and i almost did, and i put you under a lot of stress. I'm sorry. I kept my promise for two months, then everything got to be to much, and you weren't there, I couldn't talk to anyone. So I thought about it and I did, But it wasn't like before my problems didn't bleed away. I felt worse. I broke my promise to you, I know it hurts you when I do and now I regret it. I wish I hadn't , I want to stop. I just wanted you to know that I love you. My pain, you seem to feel it too. Your my reason to stop. I love you, you told me that you love me to, but as a friend not the way that I mean, that makes me want to go and slit my wrists, because I think that it hurt me more than anything...
