";“ you mock me no more shadow.” And with that he leaped and aimed a blow unto the shadow that plagued him for so long. “what of this worldly being I have not created such a monsters as yourself you credit me to much “ again he aimed and hit body slipping though the solid mass blood slipping out of his pores.<br />
"¡“ you are mistaken” &nbsp;it hissed and attacked pinning him to the be fole breath he recognized as his own seeped into his nose. “now parish rough one for the blow has been struck” &nbsp;he’s screamed where drown by the pillow that pushed tightly over his face. Suffocating him, the voices rang in his head . taughting laughter, stars appeared in the darkness, the universe was unraveling and the hole stadium was his. He gave up fighting the force and watched in sleepy dreamed as his body stopped its thrashing and twitched involuntary. His heart slowed as his breathing halted. This night became coolers of structured form. And he smiled as it engulfed him hole.<br />
